---
/**
 * <empty-block/>
 *
 * Represents an explicit empty line. Plain empty lines are stripped in Notion
 * Enhanced Markdown, so a dedicated tag is used.
 *
 * Mapped to MDX `components['empty-block']`.
 */
---
<div class="notion-empty-block" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<style>
	.notion-empty-block { height: 1.5em; }
</style>
